          <p>Keep your entire team informed on your work, with HuBoard's powerful integrations with amazing applications like <a href='https://slack.com'>Slack</a>, <a href="https://hipchat.com">HipChat</a> and <a href='https://gitter.im'>Gitter</a></p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
